EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 0800Z TO 2000Z DAILY
   20 THRU 24 NOV IN AREAS WITHIN:
   A. 30 MILES OF 57-33.4N 010-21.6W.
   B. 50 MILES OF 57-22.6N 008-49.0W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16 OR
   PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 242100Z NOV 17.
